Creator: Th3_Jugg3rn4ugh7

Players: 24

Includes lighting for terrorists (red)/ CTs (blue) to help from getting lost. 

3 story tall pillars equal spaced out and equal on all sides. Ladders only on corner pillars to reach higher levels. To reach middle pillar, must go onto 2nd floor of a corner pillar and then go to one of the left or right middle pillars and cross bridge. Then take ladder up towards middle.
